  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2e89e92c-7536-4331-a9ea-407fd9029433\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2c24b8c8-aa82-4aa4-ac02-f8c171a73544\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-dbc98240-c0c6-45d9-9a51-f2b743f6a474\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 12</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-824bef34-c531-41ee-9931-51ef86eaf665\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6e57c6e6-c7b8-4107-9a83-d741bbc73af1\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-adf0f4b2-8647-4361-902c-e833b5852968\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0fc78aa8-e804-4d30-a58e-75d936ff4b44\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[요소정리]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4ec59efc-3511-4552-8d6a-754980b2ab9e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1337fb32-a0da-432e-95a8-2c536f648d7d\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>앞으로 7일간은 주문에 필요한 인쇄의 기본적인 요소를 정리하는 시간을 갖도록 하겠습니다. 27년의 인쇄 노하우를 가진 제가 좋은 자료를 만들기 위해 본격적으로 정리한 것이니 잘 읽어보시고 인쇄 주문이나 발주시 참고하셨으면 합니다. 인쇄발주시 가장 기본이 되는 디자인 부분부터 설명하겠습니다. 시작합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-919de03f-847e-4502-bc2f-d25f3550e000\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f52ba804-efb4-4803-8670-d84101173dd2\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-e3a27ec5-ef11-40d4-b30b-0824ab33306b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c788d9c9-9d69-494b-a331-8e11070d93b3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-001ded88-71f3-48e9-82db-2858d8d1dd74\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디자인이란?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b9ac0b60-a428-4a36-9ddc-cc699bc05948\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e934d2ef-b6ad-4d2c-a9f2-602192bcbeef\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-96100c6b-4b26-4837-a8f0-4b478f428650\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://namu.wiki/w/%EB%94%94%EC%9E%90%EC%9D%B8\" target=\"_blank\">https://namu.wiki/w/%EB%94%94%EC%9E%90%EC%9D%B8</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e8dd2d42-52fe-4d32-88d8-d22f50568747\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9e37ccd9-adf3-48da-abd7-17ffa118060e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-040168d2-f8f7-4010-8e39-3ba4c691ff31\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">특히 인쇄에서 말하는 디자인은 편집디자인을 의미합니다. 시각디자인, 의류디자인, 건축디자인 등 디자인의 범위는 엄청나게 넓습니다. 하지만 종이에 표현하는 디자인을 우리는 편집디자인으로 정의하고 조금 발전된 웹디자인까지를 우리가 할 수 있는 범위라고 규정하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f0a06824-b800-4bc0-9ec0-8710d4ad418e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-af2b7bfd-7b40-4e75-b3c3-e23b506415e5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bfb24e95-eda3-4a66-9ccc-5fd3c78a46c9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222892573147/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-00f7b48c-04d8-4911-87fa-b50c79ba82c0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-77d9631d-8522-4a20-a86e-54e36bf61936\" style=\"\">편집 디자인 툴</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bb20bf67-a3f5-4a44-aece-e5070c50e3d3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d22e09e7-df81-4c71-a054-2bd014e76b8e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-61b3cba3-67da-4fdf-9e30-02bbbf98477d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-58230407-4c52-4b01-8456-eca8c424d71f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-53c2a918-5e2d-4aba-8d3b-a0b001f72682\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs30 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0fa99ff3-6a40-479e-a3d8-b12dc75cadf1\" style=\"color:#111111;\"><b>편집 디자인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e74fc522-417d-457a-af72-525b06c1135d\" style=\"line-height:1.4666666666666666;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-998eb918-c9fe-4fbe-b899-d0f148348ca6\" style=\"color:#333333;\">[ editorial design ]</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9a5c2c8a-ed27-4583-b8f5-7fdddcdd029c\" style=\"line-height:1.875;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-70c2a44c-f5dc-4d0f-8530-7e89c7a6089f\" style=\"color:#333333;\">주로 책자 형식의 인쇄물을 시각적으로 구성하여 독자에게 정보를 적절히 제공하기 위한 시각 디자인의 한 분야이다. 편집 디자인은 책의 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d0817d6a-41ae-4fac-9a30-98224bd268f4\" style=\"color:#0033ac;\">지면</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9c5c0d7f-d5da-4074-912d-e6788c2e44dc\" style=\"color:#333333;\">을 디자인하는 의미 뿐만 아니라, 독자의 독서 행위를 고려하면서 글과 사진 및 일러스트레이션, 책의 구조적인 디자인, 인쇄와 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f7e03371-4db4-45e4-a01d-f130fd2ab3eb\" style=\"color:#0033ac;\">제본</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4793e50c-2a45-4377-8a46-73910734aaf2\" style=\"color:#333333;\"> 방식을 결정하는 포괄적 디자인 행위를 지칭한다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f305077d-0923-48f2-a5f1-d25d009548c1\" style=\"line-height:1.875;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d879782b-22b6-48cc-920c-a9d44d91f27c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-21294bbf-e622-42bd-a2a5-527079acd182\" style=\"line-height:1.875;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b2d625ae-0f09-4c94-8ba8-cbe67c3ebbc4\" style=\"color:#333333;\">편집 디자인이라는 용어는 1920년대 미국에서 쓰이기 시작하면서 초기에는 잡지 디자인으로 대표되었으나, 사회문화적 환경의 변화와 기술과 매체의 다양화에 따라 잡지, 신문, 책, 브로슈어 등 다양한 인쇄물로 범위가 확대되고 편집 디자인의 의미 역시 확장되었다. 편집 디자인은 출판 디자인(publication design)과 같은 말로 쓰이기도 하는데, 일반적으로 신문 디자인(newspaper design), 잡지 디자인(magazine design), 책 디자인(book design), 브로슈어(brochure), 카탈로그(catalogue) 등의 소형 인쇄물 디자인(small printed design) 등의 분야로 구분된다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-77450274-1c5a-41ef-a6a4-5ec3f0744ec3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs11 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ded457d7-caae-4509-8b98-5655a0456942\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>편집디자인의 요설ㄹ[네이버 지식백과]</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs11 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1ccfec6f-8875-431f-9af0-6fc6935f938d\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs11 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-bd2cf9f9-2c97-4143-805b-9bc21446dc38\" style=\"color:#0033ac;\">편집 디자인</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs11 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9c21e35c-b0bb-4060-b471-85d436125565\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> [editorial design] (한글글꼴용어사전, 2000. 12. 25., 세종대왕기념사업회)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0ae18c12-7009-4bfa-a1fb-89759100b629\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-da4d6292-a94b-46c3-9c66-a3030e972872\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a36167ce-073b-4562-b70d-29284b665be5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-0477bfb4-fd36-48ae-92a0-3b9e4eea8142\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e4190ffc-9e67-4c84-a22d-47377487b3dc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b58d95b3-8044-4ebb-bbf9-b51a16f4e56c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>편집디자인의 요소</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8f563103-4268-4c93-ab07-509371661d8b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-09bb6a22-f201-448e-a55f-43fc5f32b746\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ed8e4622-b0e5-45e0-9d28-3ebb092a797a\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>사이즈</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-173aa925-29db-4f61-8d92-91d0e1e7ddc9\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5a24cf71-9c6f-4856-90e7-8d1cae7dc27a\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">디자인을 시작할 때 초보자들이 가장 오류를 많이 범하는 부분이 사이즈(규격)에 대한 부분입니다. 일단 본인이 만들고 싶은 상품의 사이즈를 가장 정확하게 알고 파악해야 합니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a8f46c0a-ad53-4f9b-8696-356301246c9a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-001f54a5-098c-4ffd-b80d-601476552e3e\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">25주차에 페이지와 사이즈 개념을 정확하게 설명할 예정입니다. 오늘은 그림으로만 간단하게 표현합니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b7ec801f-9a23-4edb-ab8a-2737cdab427e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-57568571-1a18-4c1d-a48a-086b10a6962e\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-91dcdf5f-a437-4fd7-8566-76720c9e0ac0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:749px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222892573147/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2bb6b1de-e123-44ea-8e86-a6fe49766328\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-fffd4ad2-90b2-4ab4-9976-8d33d07e41c3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d97c1ee7-afcb-4461-954e-5bb7aa6e0d10\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-328264f9-1f1a-474a-ae70-bc64679f2a49\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-334384d6-9ba1-4832-81e3-00c65656b2af\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a5dc9323-2238-4f5a-806f-dae9a7e55969\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-55665e96-25ba-42de-b925-a406b3cf593b\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-bd070820-8bb1-421d-85dd-c2a705d54773\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fd18f7c5-c6df-4bee-a0a0-5a980f73cf1a\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>레이아웃</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0e1d8102-1c3e-4776-81a3-c1fd2444100e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5d8d3d26-16c9-4e3a-b7f5-2cce9e56a7cd\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b></b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-25fb019f-335e-4ed1-9720-7d0fbd55da8d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2fdcc3d3-3bdf-4351-9fec-e7ab034d0722\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2af85360-1491-49ac-8d89-1ce771ef3ae2\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">레이아웃은 편집디자인 요소중에 하나입니다. 기본적인 틀을 말하며 사이즈안에 내용을 어떻게 표현하는지를 구상하는 시작입니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1c43de6b-8edc-421c-9a99-ea3d112f6598\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a42c67eb-071a-4c07-8146-4e5ec59f13f0\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">레이아웃은 보는 사람이 편한 구도를 잡아 디자인하며 이 구도를 여러가지로 템플릿화 해서 만드는 경우도 있습니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d5e6d637-4166-466d-a01f-6d99f62bd15d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-bc4f0b90-719c-48ff-a9b7-e4aa051086e5\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">비단 편집디자인에서만 사용하는것이 아니라 웹디자인시에도 와이어 프레임 형태로 레이아웃을 잡고 스토리보드를 작성하는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d7a090fb-fdde-4469-b846-407769244950\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8f1e6d56-10ff-4541-b130-adf60571e73a\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c6f611f9-3be6-470a-92a8-98f4603f3f10\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222892573147/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-db57425a-c9f2-4ef5-8920-547bb24ad31d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-6e20ad9d-e87c-4472-8063-c06ac845b7bb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-99b76039-4790-41de-bc2e-d2baa9d5b892\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8c42b82a-30da-469c-b8cb-2228615676a6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b4242f02-8056-4014-b120-5d9cdf72a260\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-32f645e0-8b7a-4edb-bd1d-e1cf0b931768\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-81d4bbbd-c2f2-477a-a7eb-ff7bad1acc93\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-958cf954-0a7d-4ad6-b710-ab9ad79b58ce\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b7a013c1-dcfa-45a4-80f1-892aaadfe315\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>텍스트 &amp; 폰트(서체)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b38e2614-2d28-422c-bdee-750271c5ff5d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8d87df36-d2a4-4759-8a1c-f83ae8734944\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-98733dab-36e0-4f4d-89a8-104e866d6298\" style=\"color:#559bfa;\"><b>Basic 고교생을 위한 국어 용어사전</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4491957e-1725-49a1-812c-2bdebc485c97\" style=\"line-height:1.5333333333333334;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs30 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-270100d2-b404-4576-acff-5bbcda2fd501\" style=\"color:#111111;\"><b>텍스트</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-aff5386c-484b-4ef4-9e9e-6c022ed99dde\" style=\"line-height:1.4666666666666666;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d9822ad7-6861-4580-9a01-5c1af024e616\" style=\"color:#333333;\"><b>[ text</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-32a3de8f-6ab5-44b7-b95b-ce06eff7ec23\" style=\"color:#0033ac;\"><b>음성듣기</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7c34f3f6-0a9b-4bc8-8e26-e48d27420f4d\" style=\"color:#333333;\"><b> ]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-50428b32-620d-45cd-811a-b22bfdbc605a\" style=\"line-height:1.875;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-35cb3c0f-3a28-4864-8c45-f673ac191cfe\" style=\"color:#333333;\"><b>일관되게 엮어진 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-32fbb3e1-b3d7-4da8-8768-4d11aa115ec9\" style=\"color:#0033ac;\"><b>기호</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0795357c-2824-488b-b75f-9a9f9a3f009d\" style=\"color:#333333;\"><b>의 복합체로 규정할 수 있다. 좁은 의미의 텍스트는 기호 가운데 특히 구어 혹은 문어 등의 언어로 이루어진 복합체를 뜻한다. 모든 인문과학이 그 대상으로 인간의 사유를 문제삼는다고 할 때, 사유를 표출한 결과물인 텍스트는 인문과학의 유일한 현실적 대상으로 간주될 수 있다는 점에서 그 의미는 지대하다. 롤랑 바르트(Roland Barthes)에 따르면 문학 작품(work)은 공간의 한 부분을 차지하는 실체의 단편이지만, 텍스트는 방법론적인 영역으로 그 자체로는 무의미하며 작업이나 생산에 의해서만 체험될 수 있는 것이다. 이는 전통적인 작품 개념을 텍스트로 대체함으로써 경외하고 찬탄해야 할 대상이 아닌, 적극적으로 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1ee999f4-f868-4d40-9ac1-50e1ad48b0c8\" style=\"color:#0033ac;\"><b>분석</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-258a9098-07bd-4dfe-b0ef-65b24890cae7\" style=\"color:#333333;\"><b>하고 해석해야 하는 대상으로 전환하는 것이다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bc3be840-28c9-4909-a646-43303441a2a3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs11 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-94b29bc4-319b-45b2-bf88-bca965b04f66\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>[네이버 지식백과]</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs11 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-26628615-c47d-4c4b-928b-0eab7964ebf0\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs11 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-79f6df4f-2ee7-4108-aec1-26a33b3db5ee\" style=\"color:#0033ac;\">텍스트</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs11 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8eec1a07-2f37-426f-bff7-b1d6bfb9e872\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> [text] (Basic 고교생을 위한 국어 용어사전, 2006. 11. 5., 구인환)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-530a6fac-8a62-4128-ba76-76edcf915786\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c8262424-92ea-47e3-a1a8-aa4053586380\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ff8179d5-53f5-4a14-87ae-1867aa123db3\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-00f1edbe-612d-4d0f-8398-d460b34c6970\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c018b567-f74c-4486-bc00-7c32b761199c\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">텍스트는 사전적으로는 위의 내용이지만 편집디자인에서는 본문의 내용을 말합니다. 텍스트를 표현하기 위해서는 기본적으로 폰트로 구성된 글씨로 표현되며 서체의 종류는 엄청나게 많습니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-741ad719-1093-4ef1-babc-67ae0b485253\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9adcb8ba-86e5-4d56-a82d-9d3b2375c1bd\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">본문의 내용을 txt나 다른 형태로 전달 받고 그 컨셉에 맞게 폰트를 구성하는것이 디자이너의 역할이기도 합니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-cd87b706-3e8c-4964-b4a6-438296f525ec\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d149c9f8-a966-417f-90d1-c50bef065494\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-06a0b942-1516-43eb-ae3b-456494e07a7a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-97867de1-2f5a-4506-afd0-31839842b78d\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">다음은 무료서체를 제공하거나 공유하고 알려주는 유용한 사이트입니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-426a6b78-e14b-42a9-bc7c-d2872d5dc11c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-94febe64-489f-4ed4-b765-66704214dde7\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://noonnu.cc/\" target=\"_blank\">https://noonnu.cc/</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8edf3fa1-695b-4a98-b131-16e6af79e3ec\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-511ba190-d8ef-4e7b-a984-730832e74133\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-25fd1f41-208b-4143-ab4f-d2105e04b1cd\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-6b8ebb13-9255-4258-bf61-934b65b49137\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-16f1333b-5b56-42af-b03f-15f7446afb6d\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-882e062e-89bd-4b9a-b08b-bf74ff311e15\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-39ed34b4-1bfd-485f-938a-4141b9a4328f\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이미지, 사진(포토)</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4dfa8540-57be-455c-a2d5-5d2c900697af\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1d71e2b6-41c5-4ee1-a980-9dfe7f4347dd\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">편집디자인의 가장 큰 요소중에 하는 사진의 조작과 배열 그리고 컨셉에 맞게 구성하는 작업입니다. 의뢰한 고객으로부터 받는 경우도 있고 작업하는 회사가 컨셉에 맞는 이미지를 구매 혹은 제작하여 표현할 수도 있습니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-5d6273cb-9e70-4f81-bac1-27a26137a4c5\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c094ec93-5cbd-4362-96b1-a9f345262b7e\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">사진을 편집하는 툴로는 대표적으로 포토샵 프로그램이 있습니다. 그외에 많은 그래픽 프로그램이나 템플릿 사이트들이 존재합니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f2d7f489-9a02-4ecd-a6a4-8cff72a4047e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e29c4807-a8e0-4da5-9516-cf0eba977ce0\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">기본적으로 디자인을 할때는 배경(Background Image)이나 기타 실제 이미지들로 구분할 수 있으며 그 요소들은 Vector Image로 나눠 디자인될 수 있습니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ab2260f2-e939-4444-beb6-656f7a1cf6bb\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5f969535-181d-441a-b868-e1913822e1ff\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ad57820d-cb2b-41fb-87ea-4ef8dc4fa4e7\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-881585f9-865e-4172-b3eb-6c6448b8ad38\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">다음은 무료 또는 유료사진이나 일러스트등의 이미지를 받을 수 있는 사이트들입니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7cc574e5-a705-4251-88b5-dfc0f6ed09fb\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-20fcbe15-3225-4b3d-bf1b-d5d9d55a3487\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e1c7cc81-f945-41f8-969d-21c34369658d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b742baab-369d-41e9-a282-7f98a58054ce\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">unsplash</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4bef8ec2-6d01-4fd1-b06c-57e8f36793d6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-648f1b1a-541e-45a6-ab93-7880972ba27f\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://unsplash.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://unsplash.com/</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c1eed7d0-1149-4fe9-a21b-053ef34c0a32\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-262e3a2c-f16c-4856-a8fa-ac1d6e2e0e75\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d89d0367-60a9-4245-a6b5-24b890ecb535\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">BURST</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-df4421b9-7f4c-4368-a7db-a6bc9e4f063a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c2e71804-68ba-4dd6-a2b9-2f8890693662\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://burst.shopify.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://burst.shopify.com/</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5b32e751-97ba-481b-b909-7b1c387a295c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4bf6a1f6-90db-4b02-b9dd-5b119508a8a2\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-66cf485e-e58a-46b4-8118-02d92fba51de\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">freepik</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4d1cbaee-2c8c-4cfd-bef3-43f76d210960\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-11baeb3c-b44d-48b0-80c1-b71f427fe099\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://www.freepik.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.freepik.com/</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-866c522e-a093-4ea6-8cfe-bcd7d6ef0160\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7eee5806-6e09-4327-9e70-7ca7708dd256\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cab86cd8-54de-4975-bde6-b0338886d7b4\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8c669a96-3f66-4afc-ba14-d8958ba8c122\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8254d29a-a8f6-4b93-888c-1bd032b4f21a\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">다만 위 사이트들은 모두 외국 사이트라서 한국형이미지에 약간의 제약이 있습니다. 그래도 열심히 서치해서 잘 찾으시기를 바랍니다. 또한 유료이미지 사이트는 많이 있습니다. 이 사이트는 추후 논의드리겠습니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c4638888-7b0e-48c1-bf32-935c209b1660\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-be8186b4-d1f8-4382-911d-fff143ed66ac\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a93edd9a-2bd6-4444-ba0c-643fb65f04e6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f04c2dcd-a8ca-4119-99d0-9ff9e08036c0\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a0d5d309-bde5-4c4f-85d9-0c550705a726\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1fd08dea-0e15-4f17-8b99-915509274144\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>필수자료 : 회사정보, 로고, 기타 기존의 자료들</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-711f3fee-458c-4904-b8ee-594ceabdaf78\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-911b898d-6fe3-4906-a6d4-120fb04a0596\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">디자인할 때 고객에게서 받아야하는 필수는 회사 로고입니다. 회사의 로고는 pdf, ai, cdr등의 Vector 파일로 받는것이 좋습니다. png나 jpg 같은 Bitmap형태의 이미지는 확대나 변형시 깨질 수 있습니다. 주의하시기 바랍니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-6eabe1df-7f07-4060-87da-3bace1d16a8f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ce348e7e-0915-4a02-9ddd-79b5bb8371f5\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">디자인에 도움되는 회사의 정보는 많으면 많을수록 좋습니다. 주소, 이메일, 결제정보, 기존의 브로슈어나 카다로그 자료등등은 그 회사의 컨셉을 이해하는데 도움이 많이 됩니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2b9a7da1-b1cb-4d5e-ac75-0b287f3a4913\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-df9fb09e-1f6b-4bb3-a8bb-10a2f3a9d46a\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">디자인의 비용은 고객, 회사, 내용, 기간등에 따라 가변적입니다. 이 부분은 고객과의 상담을 통해 결정됩니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니도 많은 상담 경험을 토대로 작업을 진행하고 있습니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4f44be71-b01a-44e0-bbae-f5503e72b893\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2efe2f3b-0a8e-46b1-8c96-f67f6b340f5e\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-8300d5a4-6678-4ad2-8073-68bb61d5200b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bc2531e3-b391-4b2c-ae7d-48315152486f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c155f25b-2a34-46ea-811b-f618b209adec\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>벡터(Vector), 비트맵(Bitmap) 이미지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3779d581-81ed-4c3e-b2aa-68ea0079f301\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f19d5c3d-b2b2-4b07-a849-04940ccc74cd\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-984e0fbb-a153-413d-91e6-a42f8d76cfd3\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip 1</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-76e657fb-ed6f-4638-8e7f-86c56c6efcd0\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6212ca00-05af-4784-8f7a-50b67d9c1276\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">흔히 말해 일러스트 프로그램으로 형성되는 파일은 벡터의 형식을 가지며 포토샵으로 작업된 파일들은 비트맵형식을 가지게 됩니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-cf689884-4f77-466e-86f4-1df4f662415d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f32ad612-9b22-4105-9ab9-c57ab97b87d0\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">벡터는 크기의 변화에 따라 이미지 손상이 없는 계산에 의해 이미지가 처리되는 방식이며 비트맵은 dpi(dot per inch)라는 점의 갯수로 이미지를 만들어 내는 방식입니다. 그러기 때문에 이미지를 확대하면 그 영역에서의 점의 갯수가 줄어들어서 해상도는 적어져 눈으로 볼때 상태가 떨어져 보이는 느낌을 받을 수 있습니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-dfce5f97-b271-40c0-af2a-19d5cd91746c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d25722c2-cdfd-48d5-8ab6-cdf77fb21d99\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-40394a49-6677-4383-8836-fece98b4c034\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:739px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222892573147/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-24a8f2f3-508d-4853-a5cf-741346565ad4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-bf00c9c3-254f-49db-a5fe-017882755fd7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fefdbb60-6b82-4de5-b936-26a994280c07\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7cacc961-01a5-40d3-8887-5e7bc244c571\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7d137af1-40a4-44fa-a8ef-593bd9ee9a24\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">이런 현상을 없애기 위해 로고자료는 Vector방식의 파일로 주문받아야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-65ef1ba2-63c8-4287-a580-5f35f3260807\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-72628f34-a18a-41f0-9afc-4c8cee05a1f1\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-36ef73be-dfd6-45ff-bc0e-1183e70478be\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-df2b262d-9d1e-49d7-86ff-fe09ef9fef68\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-48166ea0-17d9-4a21-b075-3cb22481b460\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d78ba6d9-7689-4973-a6df-3ff740d88dd8\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip 2</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a8db04fd-c234-4e75-bf28-753a2ace9e01\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-aac9c893-ca96-4fc9-bc83-1d0b0cf12609\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">비트맵 배경 제거 프로그램 공유</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f555cf28-5aa6-4b3d-a2ef-b2277c48a0f5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-53ddc06b-c2c8-429d-a703-21ffe2a08f2b\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://www.remove.bg/ko\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.remove.bg/ko</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-aaac64a9-706f-40ea-ad72-6f517683da25\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-07fa5843-a5fc-480f-b721-78255bd0d092\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-7360d1c1-46fb-494d-8032-5f4ccfc91143\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>다음 글의 내용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4487ebd2-7aee-4d9f-9d32-23c2a19a445a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-740b8643-bdaf-4668-817c-b8111bd82370\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9880338b-63bc-4629-a956-ccf575a18a3c\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[자료] 요소 분석 [디자인 Part2]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e9697d62-0625-474b-8033-8cbd191fea3b\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4ec4932b-9fc9-481a-b7bc-2d23b7f56b14\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-157ff320-972a-409a-9404-e773fdd3fb88\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-320b3c87-326d-4487-be91-7b9306caec7e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>디자인 주문을 받을 때 주의해야 하는 사항을 점검하겠습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8ca998d3-61f7-406a-9755-709f13ea2ddc\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-25d19dff-1183-4f62-8f4a-c1039ce80808\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-fbd59fa6-cb9d-4fe8-a315-4d19a10ac211\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8fe17a7c-bd78-4244-b15c-be3f4bed2376\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3821e1c7-711e-4ea4-af93-4662560207b1\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-03df9234-d701-4d93-abce-9f0fd35ad4db\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2569de92-5099-4c8c-b57d-b0e9be1917b7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:736px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222892573147/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-19a56faf-8231-4804-a27c-bfca069ce384\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6612cb1a-27a2-4eca-839f-011c747d7923\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c6dc3dc0-2af1-47c2-9a45-9358adf42cd4\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
